## LTM Disabled

Do not run `ltm/bin/ltm.py`, do not read `ltm/runtime/active-context.json`,
and do not create LTM checkpoints.

Use `specs/`, `docs/progress/`, git status, and the user's latest instruction
as the current source of task state.
